video.title: Selling Sunset
video.synopsis: The elite agents at The Oppenheim Group sell the luxe life to affluent buyers in LA. Relationships are everything, and that often means major drama.

episodes.synopsis: New agent Chrishell joins The Oppenheim Group and realizes she must prove herself. The brokers square off to sell a spectacular Hollywood Hills home.
episodes.title: If Looks Could Sell

episodes.synopsis: The agents get real about juggling love and career. Mary is shaken at her anniversary dinner. Heather feels the distance from Nick -- and Christine.
episodes.title: Can't Have Your Cake and Eat It Too

episodes.synopsis: Mary gets a big surprise as Christine finds herself in an unexpected fight -- and date. Actor Taye Diggs tours a home. Heather copes with a crisis.
episodes.title: (Real) Diamonds Are a Girl's Best Friend

episodes.synopsis: Chrishell learns a few lessons about business and friendship while Heather takes flak for delays. Maya makes a discovery but needs to keep it secret.
episodes.title: Loose Lips Sink Relationships

episodes.synopsis: Heather and Christine face off over the firm's big deal as Mary tries to find common ground. Christine warns Chrishell: Secrets set off explosions.
episodes.title: The One That Got Away

episodes.synopsis: A client pits Chrishell and Christine against each other. Heather sells her hot property and eyes a buyer for the unique home in the Hollywood Hills.
episodes.title: Real Estate Hunger Games

episodes.synopsis: Relationships are everything as Chrishell struggles to find an ideal home for a demanding buyer. Christine and Heather try to work together on a deal.
episodes.title: It Takes Two to Make a Thing Go Right

episodes.synopsis: Chrishell encounters jealousy as Heather embarrasses Jason. Mary reveals her frustration, and simmering tensions come to a full boil at the big party.
episodes.title: The Gloves Come Off

episodes.synopsis: The agents catch up at the $44 million home and learn Christine's engaged. Heather reveals a romance. Chrishell works the Valley. Amanza arrives.
episodes.title: Let the Real Estate Games Begin

episodes.synopsis: Chrishell and Christine have it out. Mary finds a dream home, and Davina thinks big. News of Heather’s latest love leads to a frank talk with Brett.
episodes.title: Billionaires Have Compounds

episodes.synopsis: Heather and Amanza connect before Romain drops a bombshell. Chrishell gets a key listing as Christine plans her engagement party and spills to Davina.
episodes.title: Sorry, Not Sorry

episodes.synopsis: A stressed Mary must secure a wedding venue stat. Chrishell and Christine consider the unthinkable. Tempers flare at a red-hot engagement party.
episodes.title: The Red Engagement Party

episodes.synopsis: Chrishell tours Jason's celebrity-owned home for her star client. Mary confronts Christine and battles the boss. Maya checks out Brett's project.
episodes.title: I’m No Soldier

episodes.synopsis: Retail therapy gives Christine a chance to vent. Mary shops for her ideal wedding dress. Amanza tries to help Heather, but can she do anything right?
episodes.title: The Wait Will Be Worth the Wait

episodes.synopsis: Amanza confides in Mary. Davina ponders an invitation. The agents dish the dirt in Los Feliz. After hours, the bachelorette bash seethes with drama.
episodes.title: That’s Why They Call It Real Estress

episodes.synopsis: The realtors get real and revisit the "overlap" flap. Tears at a broker's open lead to a blowout. On her big day, Mary juggles her work and wedding.
episodes.title: Karma’s Gonna Get You

episodes.synopsis: Amanza breaks down the backstabbing. After touring a sexy new listing and getting a tarot reading, Christine lashes back at her birthday bash.
episodes.title: Back to Business

episodes.synopsis: Business is booming, but Jason isn't happy with Amanza. Brokers turn out for Christine's burgers and Botox blowout. Alone, Chrishell and Davina clash.
episodes.title: Confidence Is Key

episodes.synopsis: Tensions grow over a high-priced listing, and fissures appear in a friendship. Heather and Amanza warily team up. Mary makes a confession to Romain.
episodes.title: The Biggest Agent in the Room

episodes.synopsis: The agents dish about favoritism and weigh their options. Heather and Amanza get — and give — some bad news. Friendsgiving brings a huge announcement.
episodes.title: Everybody Loves Mary

episodes.synopsis: A "Versace house" is on the agenda. Christine falls for a wedding gown. Two agents try to talk it out. After Chrishell's event, shocking news breaks.
episodes.title: Bad News Travels Fast

episodes.synopsis: Still raw, Chrishell confides in Mary. Christine, Maya and Davina meet for tea. Mary faces Romain. Amanza and Heather's teamwork makes for dream work.
episodes.title: One Text Changes Everything

episodes.synopsis: It takes two. Chrishell regroups and reassesses in St. Louis as Christine gets set for her wedding. After all her hard work, Amanza clinches a deal.
episodes.title: Two Sides to Every Story

episodes.synopsis: Chrishell returns. Heather bristles. After showing a Neutra to "Queer Eye" star Karamo, Christine walks down the aisle. Unanticipated drama awaits.
episodes.title: A Not So White Wedding

episodes.synopsis: An expecting Christine and revived Chrishell eye sexy, luxe properties. A hot market means major growth as disarming new agent Vanessa joins the team.
episodes.title: Very High Heels to Fill

episodes.synopsis: Drama looms following a tour of French Montana's opulent digs when Vanessa bonds with Christine and then connects with Chrishell, Heather and Mary.
episodes.title: New Friends, Old Enemies

episodes.synopsis: Jason breaks the news: Emma will fill her rival's sky-high heels. Chrishell fights to buy her first home. Christine talks about a tough childbirth.
episodes.title: Rival Arrival

episodes.synopsis: Another dinner, another dramatic reveal: Emma tells her side of the story. Amid spectacular views, Vanessa tries to get to the truth with Christine.
episodes.title: The Emma Dilemma

episodes.synopsis: Christine flexes for Davina, who reaches out to Jason. After a splashy sale goes south, a familiar face crashes Mary's canine birthday celebration.
episodes.title: Let Sleeping Dogs Lie

episodes.synopsis: Newly minted superhero Simu Liu gets the star treatment as Chrishell's client. Christine and Emma try to clear the air. Davina negotiates a return.
episodes.title: A House for a Hero

episodes.synopsis: Agents bring the heart — and movers, the heat — to the once-homeless Chrishell's housewarming. Amanza reveals her troubles, and a date grows awkward.
episodes.title: Back on the Market

episodes.synopsis: Chrishell takes Simu on a hero's journey through a gamer's retreat. Heather makes a tearful decision. Christine surprises Maya as Amanza gets a shock.
episodes.title: The Truth Hurts

episodes.synopsis: Open house, open book: Davina faces Christine, who meets Vanessa's mindset coach. Chrishell works with player Thomas Bryant. Mary and Romain clash.
episodes.title: The Beginning of the End

episodes.synopsis: Anticipation builds for Jason's lavish bash. Chrishell finds an ideal house for Thomas. Big news drops, but will Christine drop her defenses for Mary?
episodes.title: One Last Hail Mary
